{"id"=>228, "name"=>"Project Renewal", "category"=>"Basic Needs", "website"=>"http://www.projectrenewal.org/programs-overview", "notes"=>"Project Renewalâ€™s mission is to end the cycle of homelessness by empowering men, women and children to renew their lives with health, homes and jobs.\r\n\r\n1) Health Services:\r\n- Dental clinic\r\n- Rehab\r\n- HIV support \r\n- Occupational therapy\r\n- Optometry\r\n- Psychiatry\r\n- Psychiatric outreach team\r\n- Radiology\r\n- Primary care\r\n- Detox\r\n- Recovery center\r\n\r\n2) Homes Services:\r\n- Emergency housing\r\n- Transitional housing\r\n- Permanent housing\r\n\r\n3) Job Services", "phone"=>"212-620-0340", "address"=>"200 Varick Street\r\nNew York, NY 10014", "contact"=>"", "referral"=>"", "eligibility"=>"", "insurance"=>"", "created_at"=>DateTime.parse('Wed, 11 Mar 2015 20:06:36 UTC +00:00'), "updated_at"=>DateTime.parse('Wed, 11 Mar 2015 20:06:36 UTC +00:00')},
